#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc98"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts98"></a>
msgctxt "thag1.98:5.1"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ disvā sati muṭṭhā,"
msgstr "If you focus on the pleasant aspect"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.98:5.2"
msgid ""
"<span class=\"var\" title=\"piyanimittaṃ (bj, s2, s3, pts1)\" id=\"note66\">"
"Piyaṃ nimittaṃ</span> manasikaroto;"
msgstr "Of sights that you see, you’ll lose your mindfulness."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.98:5.3"
msgid "Sārattacitto vedeti,"
msgstr "Experiencing it with a mind full of desire,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.98:5.4"
msgid "Tañca ajjhosa tiṭṭhati;"
msgstr "You keep holding on."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.98:5.5"
msgid "Tassa vaḍḍhanti āsavā,"
msgstr "Your defilements grow,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.98:5.6"
msgid ""
"<span class=\"var\" title=\"bhavamūlā bhavagāminoti (bj, mr)\" id=\"note67\""
">Bhavamūlopagāmino”ti</span>."
msgstr "Leading to the root of rebirth in some state of existence."

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
